@Entity public class GTNetLastprice extends BaseID<Integer>
Intraday price data for instruments in the GT-Network pool. This entity stores normalized OHLCV (Open, High, Low, Last, Volume) data for instruments that are shared between GTNet peers. Each record references a GTNetInstrument which identifies the security or currency pair.

Data Flow

  1. Provider instances update this table with current market data from their connectors
  2. Consumer instances query providers and receive price updates
  3. Updates are applied based on timestamp comparison (newer wins)

Relationship to Instrument Pool

Each GTNetLastprice record has a 1:1 relationship with a GTNetInstrument. The instrument provides the identification (ISIN+currency for securities, from/to currency for pairs), while this entity stores the actual price data.
